    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Septonema lohmanii G. Delgado & O. Koukol, sp. nov. (BPI 910175, holotype): A, conidiophores, branches and conidia; B, acute apices of young co- nidiophores and branches. Scale bars: 20 μm." ;
